---

## 🧠 Reflection Prompt

> ✅ *Are you managing POA&Ms reactively or proactively?*  
> If you’re only responding to overdue deadlines, you're behind. A great GRC leader leads **from the front**, not the finish line.

---

## 🏁 Summary

- Execution is about people, process, and follow-through
- GRC leaders drive POA&M performance with clarity and consistency
- Your ability to manage risk *in motion* defines your operational maturity

